    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/508112e9c75cf2f5902bd0db3f0137fe.poster.avif?t=1770838857\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/508112e9c75cf2f5902bd0db3f0137fe.webm?t=1770838857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/508112e9c75cf2f5902bd0db3f0137fe.mp4?t=1770838857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>以原<i>《要塞》</i>系列游戏机制所开发的“要塞2”中，你可以随心所欲地享受你的田园城堡生活，也可以在烽火连连的战斗中留下你征服的铁迹。城堡管理上，对生活不满意的臣民会为非做盗，但我们必须惩罚他们。对外军事上，敌方领主正以他们的名义兴兵而起，向你的城堡步步逼近，这注定会是一场血战！城外飞石连弩，城倾人仰马翻；城内塔楼间，侵入的敌军与防御者们展开了激烈的肉搏！金盔亮甲，刀光剑影，厮杀声不绝于耳......“要塞2 Steam版”允许玩家在Steam平台上展开多达8名玩家的联网对战，也可以在离线的王位争夺模式中与电脑对手练习作战技巧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam版</h2><br>仅为Steam平台量身打造，<i>要塞2 Steam版</i>现已发布。此次更新支持Steam多人对战、成就系统、全新地图包、数字艺术读本、音轨以及可集换式卡牌。不仅如此，Steam版同时融合Steam创意工坊功能，供玩家享受与朋友们共享自制地图之乐趣！要塞2生动形象地重现了中世纪史诗般的梦幻城堡与战场，还在等什么，快收入这枚耐玩大作吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/1537692b794e61ecb73dd9724cb32875.poster.avif?t=1770838857\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/1537692b794e61ecb73dd9724cb32875.webm?t=1770838857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/1537692b794e61ecb73dd9724cb32875.mp4?t=1770838857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>要塞大重铸</strong> – 享受Steam多人游戏、创意工坊、全新成就、图形优化、独占地图，以及更多精彩等你发现！<br></li><li><strong>惩罚罪犯</strong> – 对待罪犯我们绝不手软，十八般刑具供您筛选，让他们改过自新或者干脆处死！<br></li><li><strong>身临城堡生活</strong> – 城堡内生死决斗，举行奢华宴会，或者发展战争经济，围攻敌方领主。<br></li><li><strong>夺冠为王</strong> – 通过头衔、战略、武装，在“王位争夺”战中主宰全场<br></li><li><strong>自制地图</strong> – 在Steam创意工坊中，用地图编辑器创建自制地图并分享自定义剧情。<br></li><li><strong>与朋友对战</strong> – 在“王位争夺”与“死亡竞赛”模式中与多达8名玩家展开联网对战</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/21b0446ecc0d647f45537521a2112305.poster.avif?t=1770838857\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/21b0446ecc0d647f45537521a2112305.webm?t=1770838857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/40960/extras/21b0446ecc0d647f45537521a2112305.mp4?t=1770838857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
